---
title: Idempotent order placement
---
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor C as Customer
  box rgb(235, 245, 255) Storefront
    participant W as Web app
    participant O as Order API
  end
  box rgb(240, 253, 244) Core services
    participant I as Inventory
    participant P as Payments
    participant E as Event stream
  end

  C->>W: Confirm checkout
  W->>+O: POST /orders with idempotency key
  O->>+I: Reserve cart items
  I-->>-O: Reservation and expiry time

  alt Inventory is available
    critical Authorize the payment
      O->>+P: Authorize total amount
      P-->>-O: Authorization approved
    option Provider is temporarily unavailable
      O->>O: Mark order as payment pending
    end

    par Complete the customer order
      O->>O: Persist order and reservation
    and Start downstream fulfillment
      O-)E: Publish OrderConfirmed
      E--)O: Event accepted
    end

    opt Customer requested a receipt
      O-)E: Publish ReceiptRequested
    end
    O-->>W: 201 Created with order status
    W-->>C: Show confirmation and tracking
  else One or more items are unavailable
    O-->>W: 409 Conflict with alternatives
    W-->>C: Restore cart and suggest substitutes
  end

  deactivate O
  Note over C,E: Every retry reuses the same idempotency key to prevent duplicate orders.
